<p class="MsoNormal">I was wondering if the FAQ entry below is considered current opinion or perhaps a little stale. &nbsp;Is multi-threading still considered to be &#8216;lightly tested&#8217;?&nbsp; Are there known open bugs?<o:p></o:p></p>
